Package: ggpackets
Title: Package Plot Layers for Easier Portability and Modularization
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Doug", "Kelkhoff", 
        email = "doug.kelkhoff@gmail.com", 
        role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create groups of ggplot layers that can be easily migrated from
    one plot to another, reducing redundant code and improving the ability to
    format many plots that draw from the same source ggpacket layers.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    utils,
    methods,
    ggplot2,
    tibble,
    rlang
